{"tid":1593254,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"超過7000張文宣圖","createTime":"2019-09-25T03:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T14:01:50.000Z","uid":116953,"like":222,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":131,"replies":[{"pid":"46d08485fea4f580f986ecc7f116efcfdcbee3a1","tid":1593254,"uid":116953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:53:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/hongkongProtesters/boards/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pinterest.com%2FhongkongProtesters%2Fboards%2F&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9Cbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=dbe73904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pinterest.com/hongkongProtesters/boards/</a><br />\n由於越來越多文宣圖既關係<br />\n我將整個board拆散再分類方便大家搵圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EwGZi4X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEwGZi4X.png&h=2cb8d24e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為係文宣我就依宣傳對象分類<br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">活動日程 - 對象：活動宣傳</span></strong><br />\n所有活動相關文宣依日期排序，<span style=\"color: gold;\">包括所有語言</span>，部份只有一張文宣既活動無開 section，碌落D就會見到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>行動/支援/打氣 - 對象：手足</strong></span><br />\n所有長期行動，比手足睇既支援/打氣文宣，懶人包，插圖/漫畫，緊急熱線，願榮光歸香港，民間記者會，罷買，black bloc，以武制暴...等等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>港共警暴黑社會 - 對象：淺黃/正常人</strong></span><br />\n所有警暴濫權，打人殺人扮示威者，新屋嶺，黑警合作，監警會，MTR黨鐵，太子恐襲，元朗恐襲，港共林鄭政府，黑社會藍絲，白色恐怖，智能監控，社會評級，性暴力，毒氣彈，赤納粹，Yellow Object...等等<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">中立民生/柔性文宣 - 對象：淺藍/港豬/廢老/貼牆</span></strong><br />\n適合比D自稱中立人士睇既文宣，都適合貼牆，防藍撕，經濟牌，親情牌，赤化，失去自由，長輩圖...等等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>International Artwork - 對象：外國人</strong></span><br />\n就係國際文宣，所有非活動類既外語文宣，topic用左英文方便外國人直接睇，5 demands, Yellow Object, Police State, Sun UK Ling, Chinazi, Sexually Harassed, How to help HK....等等<br />\n<br />\n仲有文宣相片同GIF由於唔係主力收集所以數量不足，有機會再加多D<br />\n大家除左拎來用之外，都可以根據文宣數量去決定邊D文宣需要做多D<br />\n分類方面仲未完美但我會不停改善<br />\n各位要加油<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"cd5e0a18eebb31c24b200cc391dcd6c830b81e34","tid":1593254,"uid":47605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"aa962cabf13c2dce96a61b27098b2fc53f2aada0","tid":1593254,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:54:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ab1f81f60441b2e290c0ab796802ad2cb6c786","tid":1593254,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:55:21.000Z","msg":"[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"22c7ea7d0bab934049596a214eaa28b1606a14d2","tid":1593254,"uid":152568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:55:26.000Z","msg":"Pusy"},{"pid":"c7c87d71c166d96d4bf9a1b53a55e688ffab0fd1","tid":1593254,"uid":273886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:55:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bce16b6c367e1547c0d010d2d20e79bc8f213558","tid":1593254,"uid":13250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:04:13.000Z","msg":"正啊,終於有文宣網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f11004334b316e164e321b960dbdd328248ce3","tid":1593254,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UepWY5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUepWY5d.jpg&h=e503b768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">927 新屋嶺 928民陣集會